&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 27px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(227,108,10); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
吕文艺老师公元&lt;font FACE="楷体"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 36px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;2012&lt;/SPAN&gt;年特别奉献：&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 16px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 33pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px"&gt;
&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 33px; FonT-FAMiLY: 方正大标宋简体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: red; FonT-siZe: 22pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
 &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt;&lt;font FACE="方正大标宋简体"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/SPAN&gt;“时空掌控学”高层政商领导研修班&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 16px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 18.05pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px"&gt;
&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 27px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(64,64,64); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 27px; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: white; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(0,176,240); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"&gt;
 &lt;wbr  /&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;font STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 36px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" COLOR="#FF0000"&gt;你不掌控他人，你就会被他人掌控！&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 16px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 18.05pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px"&gt;
&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 27px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(64,64,64); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 27px; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: white; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(0,176,240); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"&gt;
&lt;font STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 36px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" COLOR="#FF0000"&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/SPAN&gt;你不掌控时空，你就会被时空毁灭！&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 16px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 27pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px"&gt;
&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 27px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(64,64,64); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;“&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 27px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(64,64,64); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;时空掌控学&lt;font FACE="华文楷体"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 36px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;”&lt;/SPAN&gt;是一门全新的学科；是一种能够高效迅速实现掌控他人和掌控自己，顺利实现自己做事目标的支持技术；是一种能够&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 27px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(64,64,64); FonT-siZe: 24px; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;迅速破解你所遇到的各种人事障碍难题的人生必修学问。&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 16px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 27.05pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px"&gt;
&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 27px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(192,0,0); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
 &lt;wbr  /&gt;“时空掌控学”绝对不是“心理&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 27px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(192,0,0); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;学”的理论技术。&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 16px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 27.05pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px"&gt;
&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 27px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(192,0,0); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
“时空掌控学”绝对不是“易经风水星座等占卜之术”。 &lt;wbr  /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 17px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 36pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px"&gt;
&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(38,38,38); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
 &lt;wbr  /&gt;它需要智慧的您在这里多停留一会儿，以深入了解这门学问！ &lt;wbr  /&gt;也许，只是一会儿，你一生的命运就会因为这全新又独特的&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: red; FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;“&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: red; FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;时空掌控学&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 36px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;&lt;font FACE="华文楷体"&gt;”&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 华文楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(38,38,38); FonT-siZe: 18pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;而变的更加灿烂辉煌！&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;						&lt;/div&gt;
										
