&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 30pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 黑体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
你不掌控他人，你就会被他人掌控！&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 30pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 黑体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
你不掌控时空，你就会被时空毁灭！&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
“时空掌控学”绝对不是心理学的理论技术！&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
“时空掌控学”是一门专门研究&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px;"&gt;“&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px;"&gt;在什么样的特定时空环境能量场，人会发生什么样的决策行为，做出什么样的决策结果”的新学科。&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
应用“时空掌控学”，不论你面对智慧水平如何强势的他人，你都可以时刻掌握主动权，时刻掌控局势发展的走向，为你争取到更多更大的政治和经济利益空间。“时空掌控学”是你创造财富帝国和权力帝国的最强大支持技术！&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
物竞天择，弱肉强食，是大自然的必然，也是人类社会的必然。身处社会政商高层的精英领袖，时刻被社会强烈关注，时刻面临政治活动和经济活动的巨大风险。掌控自己不发生错误的决策行为和做出错误的决策结果，掌控自己的人脉资源网络不出现带来灾难的问题，是每一个政商高层领导所面临的最重要日常课题。“时空掌控学”就是政商高层领导解决这一生存难题的最好学问！&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
公元&lt;font FACE="楷体"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;2012&lt;/SPAN&gt;年，“时空掌控学”的创立者吕文艺老师，将历时&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;20&lt;/SPAN&gt;多年的科研成果全面推出，服务全国高层政商领导，为各界政商精英创建财富和权力帝国提供“掌控学”的技术支持！&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
一、研修内容：&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;1&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、应用“时空掌控学”掌控自己不发生错误的决策行为和不做出错误的决策结果的理论技术。&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;2&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、应用“时空掌控学”掌控自己人脉资源网络中所有人的理论技术。&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
二、研修时间：&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;1&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、公元&lt;font FACE="楷体"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;2012&lt;/SPAN&gt;年&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;5&lt;/SPAN&gt;月&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;26&lt;/SPAN&gt;日——&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;5&lt;/SPAN&gt;月&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;29&lt;/SPAN&gt;日开课。&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;2&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、公元&lt;font FACE="楷体"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;2012&lt;/SPAN&gt;年&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;6&lt;/SPAN&gt;月——&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;12&lt;/SPAN&gt;月，每月的&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;15&lt;/SPAN&gt;日——&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;18&lt;/SPAN&gt;日开课。&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;3&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、研修内容每两月循环讲授一次，研修学习的领导可以根据自己实际情况参加任何一期的课程学习。一年内不限学习次数。&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
三、授课专家：&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
“时空掌控学”的创立者，著名学者——吕文艺老师。&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
四、研修学费：&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;1&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、报名会员资料杂费&lt;font FACE="楷体"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;2000&lt;/SPAN&gt;元。&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;2&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、研修学费&lt;font FACE="楷体"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;4.8&lt;/SPAN&gt;万元。&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
五、研修条件：&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;1&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、党政事业单位正科级以上领导干部。&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;2&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、大中型企业（公司）中高层领导。&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
六、报名方法：&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;1&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、网上填写报名资料或传真资料报名。我们收到资料后，将和你电话联系确认。&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;2&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、确认后汇报名资料等杂费&lt;font FACE="楷体"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;2000&lt;/SPAN&gt;元登记备案。备案后，有关研修学习的相关事宜，我们会及时与你联系。&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 20.25pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;3&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 楷体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;、你也可以亲自到公司报名确认并登记备案。&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
七、公司地址：&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;北京市海淀区北三环西路&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;48&lt;/SPAN&gt;号院&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;3&lt;/SPAN&gt;号楼&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;9D&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 30pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
公司电话：&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;010-56229488&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;56229499&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/SPAN&gt;传真：&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;010&lt;/SPAN&gt;－&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;82102622&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 30pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
手机：&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/SPAN&gt;18611320677&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt; &lt;wbr  /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/SPAN&gt;18601045777&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; pADDinG-BoTToM: 0px; Line-HeiGHT: 21px; BorDer-riGHT-WiDTH: 0px; LisT-sTYLe-TYpe: none; TexT-inDenT: 30pt; MArGin: 0px 0px 5px; pADDinG-LeFT: 0px; pADDinG-riGHT: 0px; WorD-WrAp: normal; BorDer-Top-WiDTH: 0px; BorDer-BoTToM-WiDTH: 0px; WorD-BreAK: normal; BorDer-LeFT-WiDTH: 0px; pADDinG-Top: 0px" ALIGN="left"&gt;&lt;span STYLE="Line-HeiGHT: 30px; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; WorD-WrAp: normal; CoLor: rgb(70,70,70); FonT-siZe: 15pt; WorD-BreAK: normal"&gt;
